================================================================================
1. Initial installation


1.1 Dependancies

1.1.1 Create a python venv whith following dependancies

Django (1.10.1)
mod-wsgi (4.5.7)
pip (8.1.2)
setuptools (20.10.1)

mod-wsgi is only needed for apache installation (production platform)


1.2 Configure Environment

1.2.1 By makefile

<vi makefile>
ROOT=<root install path directory>
</vi>

<vi django/hermesgui/settings.py>
STATIC_ROOT = '<root install path directory>/www/static'
</vi>

<sh>make</sh>

1.2.2 Manually generate static files

For platforms without make and apache httpd installed.

<sh>
mkdir -p www/static
cd django
python manage.py collectstatic --no-input
</sh>

1.3 Database tables generation

<sh>
cd django
python manage.py migrate
</sh>

1.4 Super user create

<sh>
cd django
python manage.py createsuperuser
</sh>


================================================================================
2. Configuration

2.1 Localization

<vi django/settings.py>
LANGUAGE_CODE = 'fr'
TIME_ZONE = 'Europe/Paris'
</vi>


================================================================================
3. Administration

3.1 Development server

<sh>
cd django
python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8000
</sh>


================================================================================
4. Models

4.1 Model definition

4.1.1 Model definition example

<vi django/<application/models.py>
...
class Connection(models.Model):
    name = models.CharField(max_length=30)
    host = models.CharField(max_length=30)
    protocol = models.CharField(max_length=10)
    user = models.CharField(max_length=30)
    password = models.CharField(max_length=30)
    private_key = models.FilePathField
    deleteflag = models.BinaryField
    activation = models.BinaryField
    command = models.CharField(max_length=10)
    excluderegex = models.CharField(max_length=10)
    includeregex = models.CharField(max_length=10)
    localdir = models.FilePathField()
    statuslogdir = models.FilePathField
    backupdir = models.FilePathField
    remotedir = models.FilePathField
    logfile = models.FilePathField
</vi>

4.2 Application declaration

<vi django/settings.py>
INSTALLED_APPS = [
    'connection_admin.apps.ConnectionAdminConfig',
    ...
]
</vi>

update database schema

<sh>
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate
</sh>

4.2 Model admin

add to administration interface:
<vi django/connection_admin/admin.py>
...
from .models import Connection

admin.site.register(Connection)
</vi>